e time, connect Blinq to your CRM to automatically sync and export your contacts every time they\'re updated.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#128;&#141;</p><figure class=\"w-richtext-figure-type-image w-richtext-align-center\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 60%; clear: both; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"font-size: 0px; color: transparent; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%;\"><img src=\"https://assets-global.website-files.com/617ac0d059899a69fd8216ec/63f6e97f70034c3171a7b359_62Zn5HT5EAXG5g6Z9ieOpeArmHf84GCoF0t1KP3mZpS1-CG7gAbp60T39CErSaWvwRhndnnLn7bdsGVCLfuCnmubWqmFZW1Z9ZY1r08cQTIQFRC-7ADvUwlB-Gtnxj7IsSkTbXYCR-_b8xmB8jcbI6M.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 551.688px;\"></div></figure><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#128;&#141;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&eth;&#159;&#147;&#154;Related&acirc;&#158;&iexcl;<a href=\"https://blinqapp.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/6153366301081\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">How to export Blinq contacts to a CRM</a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#128;&#141;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><em>\"Teams, especially sales and procurement teams, love that their new contacts pull through automatically and smoothly to their CRM connections without them needing to interfere at all!\"</em>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">- Travis James, Growth Operations Manager</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#128;&#141;</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">3. Automate Card Creation For Teams by Linking With Your HR Directory</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#128;&#141;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Linking your Blinq digital business card account to an active directory like Azure AD streamlines creating, updating, and distributing team cards in bulk.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#128;&#141;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">When new hires join your team and the HR directory updates, a new digital business card can automatically be generated. Promotions can also be applied to employee business cards in real-time. No need to spend resources redesigning, reprinting, and distributing cards every time there\'s an internal company change.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#128;&#141;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&eth;&#159;&#147;&#154;Related&acirc;&#158;&iexcl;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinqapp.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/4407482595993-SCIM-Provisioning-of-Users-with-Azure-AD\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">SCIM