r-free\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em;\">8. Providers like Blinq let you try them for free to make your own mind up</h3></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Imagine this scenario:</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">You pay for a large delivery of paper business cards. Upon opening the package, you discover that they don\'t meet your needs or preferences. The money you spent vanishes with no result.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">That&acirc;&#128;&#153;s the risk of paper business cards.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">No printing service offers a free trial card to let you see if the investment is worth it before you commit.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">But on Blinq\'s free plan, you get two free digital business cards with unlimited shares. You can give them out, measure their impact, and decide if you want to invest in them.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Create a&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://blinq.me/solutions/digital-business-card\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">free digital business card</a><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;on Blinq today.</span></p><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 56px; line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">How to get the most out of a digital business card</h2><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Ensure your digital business card is visually appealing and easy to read</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The design of your card should be attractive and professional to capture attention and present you as a professional.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">When designing your card, keep these in mind:</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#156;&#133; Avoid clutter: it shouldn&acirc;&#128;&#153;t be cluttered with information. Keep it clean and simple.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#156;&#133; Arrange your details hierarchically. Your name should be the first thing on your digital card. Followed by your title. And so on.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#156;&#133; Ensure the font sizes are legible</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#156;&#133; Your brand and card design should align. Add your color palette and Logo.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">You can use these&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/blog/digital-business-card-examples\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">examples of digital business cards</a>&nbsp;as a guide. We&acirc;&#128;&#153;ve also got industry-specific articles for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/blog/the-digital-business-card-real-estate-agents-love\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">realtors</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/blog/the-online-business-card-every-digital-nomad-needs\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">digital nomads</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/blog/the-digital-business-card-that-photographers-love\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">photographers</a>!</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Add a high-quality headshot</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">A great headshot exudes confidence, competence, and professionalism. It plays a huge role in determining people&acirc;&#128;&#153;s perceptions of you.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Your headshot should align with your brand, and be of high quality to avoid pixelation.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Blinq has curated a list of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/blog/professional-headshot-examples\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">15 great professional headshots</a>. You can use it as a guide.&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Include essential links</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Provide contacts with different ways to reach you.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This includes</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#156;&#133; Social media links&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#156;&#133; Links to your Website or landing page</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#156;&#133; Links to your Payment information</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#156;&#133; Links to your Scheduling pages (Calendly, Google Calendar, etc)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This way, they can contact you from your business card.&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Demonstrate expertise by linking to your eBook</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Including a link to your eBook card tells potential clients, partners, or employers you&acirc;&#128;&#153;re an expert. They will be more likely to trust you and do business with you.</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Repurpose it&nbsp;</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">There are different ways to use a digital business card.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#156;&#133; Share it in the bios of your social media accounts</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#156;&#133; Include it in your ad campaigns</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#156;&#133; Embed it on your website. We have a guide on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/blog/how-to-embed-your-digital-business-card-on-your-website\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">how to embed your digital business card on your website</a>.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&acirc;&#156;&#133; Include the QR code in your company merch</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Use it as your email signature</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">You can use your digital business cards as email signatures. This makes it simple for others to get in touch with you, while also projecting an expert image to those who receive your emails.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Blinq lets you create your email signature from your dashboard.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Simply import your details from your digital card, click save, then add it to your email account.</p><figure class=\"w-richtext-figure-type-image w-richtext-align-fullwidth\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 100%; width: 919.5px; text-align: center; clear: both; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"font-size: 0px; color: transparent; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: inherit;\"><img src=\"https://assets-global.website-files.com/617ac0d059899a69fd8216ec/63e3355258fecf90a7efd0ca_akachukwu-obialor-email-signaturre.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 630px;\"></div></figure><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Want an email signature but don&acirc;&#128;&#153;t have a Blinq account?&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://blinq.me/solutions/email-signature\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">Generate a free email signature</a></p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Share your digital business card on social media</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">You reach a wider audience and increase online visibility by sharing your digital business card on social media.</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Add your QR code to the virtual background during meetings</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">During remote meetings, you can use your digital business card&acirc;&#128;&#153;s QR code to create a virtual background.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Attendees get your digital business card when they scan the QR code.</p><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 56px; line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">What should I put on my business card?</h2><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Contact information</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This is a vital portion of your business card. Because people can&acirc;&#128;&#153;t reach you if there&acirc;&#128;&#153;s no contact information.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Your contact information includes your:</p><ul role=\"list\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 40px; overflow: hidden; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li>Name</li><li>Title and headline</li><li>Company name</li><li>Phone number</li><li>Email address</li><li>Website.</li><li>Address (virtual or physical)</li></ul><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Professional headshot (profile picture)</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">At first glance, your headshot tells if you&acirc;&#128;&#153;re someone to connect with or not. So, it&acirc;&#128;&#153;s important to use one that&acirc;&#128;&#153;s professional looking.</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Brand assets</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This includes your logo and color palette. Ensure the logo is legible and not pixelated.</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Social media links</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Include links to social media profiles. This way, people have multiple ways to connect with you.</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Additional data</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Include other relevant additional information such as skills, accreditations, meeting links, and payment links.</p><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 56px; line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">How do I create a digital business card on my phone?</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Firstly, download the Blinq application to your phone.&nbsp;</p><p><a id=\"ensure-your-digital-business-card-is-visually-appealing-and-easy-to-read\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"></a><a id=\"add-a-high-quality-headshot\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"></a><a id=\"include-essential-links\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"></a><a id=\"demonstrate-expertise-by-linking-to-your-ebook\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-family: Avenirnext, san